data.description: Great 2B/2B ranch in lovely Reed neighborhood on a dead-end street. This home lives large. Living rm w/vaulted ceilings has dual Gas/Wood fireplace & south light. Cute Kitch opens to side patio. Big Primary bed has its own patio, lots of closet space & updated bath w/custom Walnut Cabs, heated fl & walk-in shower. Thoughtful updates thru out. XL 2-Car garage. Private sideyd w/lots of gardening space; herb garden & perennial fruit plants. Just blks to shopping, coffee, parks, public transit, etc. [Home Energy Score = 5. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10195696]
